[3.789, "o", "\u001b[38;2;59;130;246m⇠ [debate-rounds.0.pro-argue]\u001b[0m \u001b[2msent to coordinator:\u001b[0m Remote work should be the default. The benefits are numerous and well-documented, impacting both employees and employers positively.\r\n\r\nFirstly, remote work enhances productivity. Studies by Stanford and Airtasker have shown that remote worke...\r\n"]
